SUMMARY:Easter Trolley Treasure Hunt at Gold Ridge Farms
DESCRIPTION:Easter Trolley Treasure Hunt at Gold Ridge Organic Farms invites families to hop aboard the farm’s charming Apple Trolley for a festive 75-minute Easter adventure. Guests will enjoy a scenic guided ride through the orchard before setting off among the apple trees to solve clues\, collect secret letters\, and unscramble a mystery word to win a prize.    Each child receives a goodie bag filled with apple snacks\, stickers\, stamps\, a puzzle pad\, and seeds to grow at home. After the hunt\, families can explore the Farm Shop and enjoy apple slushies\, ice cream with apple cider syrup\, and tastings of the farm’s house-made olive oil\, apple cider balsamic vinegar\, and apple syrup.    Reservations recommended.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/easter-trolley-treasure-hunt-at-gold-ridge-organic-farms/
LOCATION:3387 Canfield Road, Sebastopol, CA, 95472, United States
CATEGORIES:Family Friendly,Food,Holiday,Outdoors,Sonoma County
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://winecountry-media.s3.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2026/03/10235900/649733287_1485964853536576_8167140181219020620_n.jpg
