SUMMARY:Easter Egg Hunt at Coppola
DESCRIPTION:Save the date and hop over to Francis Ford Coppola Winery for the Annual Spring Egg Hunt and Carnival. The fun begins at 11:00am sharp with an egg hunt through the vineyards\, followed by a festive carnival at the winery with games and entertainment for all ages.    The Easter Bunny will be on-site for photos\, adding to the celebration. Guests are encouraged to arrive between 10:00 and 10:45am to ensure they don’t miss the hunt. Please bring a basket for collecting eggs and treats. Ticket purchases are limited to 12 per guest. No tickets are required for guests ages 13 and up. The Pool Café will be open with a special à la carte menu featuring food and beverages.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/easter-egg-hunt-at-coppola/
LOCATION:300 Via Archimedes, Geyserville, CA, 95441, United States
GEO:-122.8880721;38.6796559
CATEGORIES:Celebration,Family Friendly,Holiday,Outdoors,Sonoma County
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://winecountry-media.s3.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2026/02/04215342/ffcw-home-events-easter-egg-hunt.png
END:VEVENT
