SUMMARY:Bartholomew Adult Scavenger Hunt
DESCRIPTION:Bartholomew Estate Winery invites guests to enjoy an Adult Scavenger Hunt\, an adventurous and interactive experience across the historic estate. Teams will follow clues and complete challenges while exploring the beautiful park grounds and uncovering hidden gems along the way.    After the hunt\, celebrate your accomplishment with a relaxing wine tasting and see which teams take home prizes for finishing in the top three. It’s a fun and active way to explore the property while enjoying great wine and friendly competition.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/bartholomew-adult-scavenger-hunt/
