SUMMARY:Easter Sunrise at Cline Family Cellars
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Easter at Cline Family Cellars\, where the Cline family continues a cherished tradition of hosting a sunrise service on the winery grounds. For more than 20 years\, Fred and Nancy Cline have welcomed the community to gather for this peaceful morning celebration. Guests are invited to enjoy the service at sunrise\, followed by coffee and pastries. Reservations are recommended for this special annual event.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/easter-sunrise-at-cline-family-cellars/
LOCATION:24737 Arnold Drive, Sonoma, CA, 95476, United States
