SUMMARY:Easter Brunch at Fairmont Sonoma
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Easter in Sonoma at Santé with a festive brunch experience at Fairmont Sonoma. Enjoy a delicious spread of seasonal favorites alongside a signature dessert buffet\, perfect for the whole family.    Little ones can join the Easter Bunny for one of two charming egg hunts\, while face painting and live music by Jason Bodlovich add to the fun\, creating a lively and memorable holiday atmosphere.    Brunch is served from 10 AM to 2 PM\, with Easter egg hunts taking place at 9:30 AM and 11:30 AM. Whether you're gathering with family or friends\, this joyful celebration offers the perfect way to enjoy Easter in Sonoma.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/easter-brunch-at-fairmont-sonoma/
LOCATION:100 Boyes Blvd, Sonoma, CA, 95476, United States
GEO:-122.4825311;38.3130389
