SUMMARY:Easter Sunday at The Barlow
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Easter Sunday at The Barlow with a fun-filled afternoon at The Venue in Sebastopol. Perfect for families\, this festive event features an egg hunt with over 800 eggs for kids 12 and under\, plus photos with the Easter Bunny\, face painting\, arts and crafts\, and sidewalk chalk fun.    Spread out on the lawn and enjoy a relaxed picnic-style day with food and drinks available for purchase\, including fresh sandwiches and baked goods from Wild Poppy Cafe\, homemade apple pie\, and a mimosa bar for adults.    Your ticket includes access to all activities\, making it easy to enjoy a day of springtime celebration with loved ones. Bring a basket for the egg hunt and settle in for an afternoon of festive fun\, creativity\, and community in the heart of The Barlow.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/easter-sunday-at-the-barlow/
LOCATION:6770 McKinley Street., Sebastopol, CA, 95472, United States
GEO:-122.821687;38.4037575
CATEGORIES:Celebration,Fairs & Festivals,Family Friendly,Food,Holiday,Outdoors,Sonoma County
